cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR 

This paper deals with computer vision and robotics, specifically the problem of localizing a ground vehicle using satellite imagery. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves machine learning techniques, which suggests the category cs.LG (Machine Learning). The use of filtering frameworks and the problem of localization suggest the category cs.RO (Robotics). The paper also involves the use of neural networks, which suggests the category cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, the use of satellite imagery suggests the category cs.GR (Graphics).
